---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import GreenBlock from '../components/GreenBlock.astro';
---
<Base title="About" current="About" description="The why behind MPower. People are already capable - they just need the right tools, in the right place, in plain language.">

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mono kicker">§ The why · 2026</div>
      <h1 class="display about-h1">
        People are <span class="i-accent">already capable.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg about-lede">
        They just need the right tools, in the right place, in plain language. The world doesn't lack for expertise. It lacks people genuinely wanting to build each other up, help each other out, and equip them so they are empowered. We're on a mission to change that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <figure class="media">
        <div class="media-frame"><img src="/images/about.jpg" alt="Real people, real moments - Aotearoa." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <figcaption class="mono">§ Hands, not headshots · Aotearoa</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <span class="mono accent">§ Fig. 01 - The name encodes the journey</span>
        <h2 class="heading two-col-title">Equip you. Then empower you.</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="body-lg">
          MPowered is what people become, not what we do <em>to</em> them. The italic <span class="i-accent">2</span> in our tagline - Equip<span class="i-accent">2</span>MPower - is the bridge between knowing and doing. We equip: the knowledge, the tools, the plain-language how. The power is <span class="accent">yours</span> from there.
        </p>
        <p class="body" style="margin-top: 24px; opacity: .82;">
          No gatekeepers. No jargon. No sense that someone's talking down to you. We measure success by the day you can answer for yourself, teach someone else, and pass it on - and stay anyway, because you love the community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="mono accent">§ Who we design for</span>
      <h2 class="display audience-title">
        Real people. <span class="i-accent">Real stories.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top: 28px; max-width: 60ch; opacity: .9;">
        We're listening to your stories, your challenges, what you're wanting. What works for a person on a farm in a remote Waikato village will work for a CEO in an ivory tower - the converse is seldom true. So we design from the real, specific person out.
      </p>

      <div class="audiences">
        <article>
          <h3 class="heading">A leadership family</h3>
          <p class="body-lg">Five offerings, one ladder. MPower Agri and MPower Ed launch first. MPower Teams is here now, by arrangement. MPower Leaders and MPower Rising are coming.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3 class="heading">Built for individuals</h3>
          <p class="body-lg">One person, one membership. Buying seats for a whole organisation isn't set up yet - if that's what you're after, that's MPower Teams, by arrangement.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3 class="heading">No selling, ever</h3>
          <p class="body-lg">No ads, no sponsors, no affiliate deals inside the communities, including us upselling you. That's a promise to members, and it's not negotiable.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <GreenBlock kicker="§ Built so you don't need us anymore.">
    <h2>You were always capable. <em>Now you're equipped.</em></h2>
  </GreenBlock>

</Base>

<style>
  .kicker { color: var(--c-spring); margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .about-h1 { font-size: var(--t-h1); max-width: 18ch; }
  .about-lede { margin-top: 32px; max-width: 64ch; opacity: .9; }
  .media { margin: 0; }
  .media-frame { border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--c-rule-soft); }
  .media-frame img { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; object-fit: cover; filter: saturate(.92) brightness(.97); }
  .media figcaption { font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: var(--t-mono); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--c-fog); padding-top: 12px; }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px;
  }
  .two-col-title { font-size: var(--t-h4); margin-top: 14px; max-width: 14ch; }

  .audience-title { font-size: var(--t-h2); margin-top: 28px; max-width: 22ch; }
  .audiences { margin-top: 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 36px; }
  .audiences article {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px;
    padding-bottom: 36px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
  }
  .audiences h3 { font-size: var(--t-h3); }
  .audiences p { max-width: 56ch; opacity: .86; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .audiences article { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
